videos.description: Naji Marshall grabs the rebound and takes it all the way himself for a transition layup.
videos.headline: Marshall Euro-steps for layup

videos.description: Kevin Zabo pushes the ball up court and dumps it off to a trailing Danny Pippen for a two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Pippen skies for fast-break dunk

videos.description: Kevin Zabo misses an easy bucket, but grabs his own miss and makes the bucket.
videos.headline: Zabo makes tough layup for 3-point play
